Class ProfileActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • Activity
      • cs.ualberta.CMPUT301F14T08.stackunderflow.activities.ProfileActivity

  • public class ProfileActivity
extends Activity
    ProfileActivity This is the view for the to view profile attributes. This displays how many questions and answers a user has submitted. This also displays all of a users read later, favorites and personal posts. Finally this is also the main location where the user can view his name and change it.
    Author:
    Cmput301 Winter 2014 Group 8
